        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>2 Samuel 18</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" xml:id="Sam2018-P92r-L7" n="7"
                            prev="TKow.02.003.017.xml#Sam2017-P92r-L7" />
                        <l xml:id="Sam2-018-x001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">יח׳ </foreign>
                        </l>
                        <l n="1" xml:id="Sam2-018-001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויפקוד</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            Da sanady David osol ol ulusnu ki birgesine anyn da qojdu alar istine aɣaraqlaryn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            minlernin da aɣaraqlaryn izlernin.</l>
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Sam2-018-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וישלח </foreign>
                            Da ijdi David osol ol ulusnu osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            ol icinci ḥelekni qolu asyra Joʾavnyn da ol icinci ḥelekni qolu asyra Avišajnyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            uvlunun Cerujanyn qaryndasynyn Joʾavnyn da ol icinci ḥelekni qolu asyra Itajnyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ol Gatlynyn da ajtty meleḫ ulusqa cyqma cyɣarmen daɣyn mende birgenizge
                            siznin.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                        <l n="3" xml:id="Sam2-018-003"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty ol ulus cyqmaɣyn ki eger qacma qacsaq qojmastylar bizge
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            is da eger elseler jarymlarymyzda qojmastylar bizge es ki haligine barbiz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            bizin ceriv on minler da haligine edirek bolur ki bolsan bizge sahardan
                            bolusma.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                        <l n="4" xml:id="Sam2-018-004"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty alarɣa ol meleḫ neni ki jaḥsy<addSpan spanTo="#Sam2-018-add001"
                                 />dy<anchor xml:id="Sam2-018-add001" type="addSpan" /> kezlerinizde
                            qylarmen da turdu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            ol meleḫ janynda ol qabaqnyn da bar ol ulus cyqtylar izlerge da
                            minlerge.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                        <l n="5" xml:id="Sam2-018-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצו </foreign>
                            Da zynharlady ol meleḫ osol Joʾavny da osol Avišajny da osol Itajny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            ajtadoɣac aqyrtynlyq byla mana ulanny Avšalomnu da bar osol esittiler
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            zynharlaɣanda ol meleḫ osol aɣaraqlarny barlaryn isi icin
                            Avšalomnun.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                        <l n="6" xml:id="Sam2-018-006"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצא </foreign>
                            Da cyqty ol ulus ol tizge utrusuna Jisraʾelnin da edi ol ceriv orma-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            nynda Efrajimnin.</l>
                        <l n="7" xml:id="Sam2-018-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וינגפו </foreign>
                            Da ḥastalandylar anda ulusu Jisraʾelnin alnynda
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            qullarynyn Davidnin da edi anda ol qyranc ullu ol kinde ol egirmi
                            min.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                        <l n="8" xml:id="Sam2-018-008"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ותהי </foreign>
                            Da edi anda ol ceriv tozulɣanlar izleri istine bar ol jernin da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            artyqraq etti kijigi ol ormannyn asama cerivni ulusta neden ki tavustu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            ol qylyc ol kinde ol.</l>
                        <l n="9" xml:id="Sam2-018-009"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקרא </foreign>
                            Da ucraldy Avšalom alnynda qullarynyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            Davidnin da Avšalom atlanyredi ol cuval istine da keldi ol cuval butaɣy
                            <milestone unit="page" n="92v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            tibine ol lipanyn ol ullu da tutundu basy anyn lipadan da berildi arasyna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            ol keklernin da arasyna ol jernin da ol cuval ki anyn tibine asty.</l>
                        <l n="10" xml:id="Sam2-018-010"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וירא</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            Da kerdi bir kisi da anlatty Joʾavɣa da ajtty muna kerdim osol Avšalomnu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            asyladoɣanny lipadan.</l>
                        <l n="11" xml:id="Sam2-018-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty Joʾav kisige ol anlatuvcuɣa anar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            da muna kerdin da ne icin vatmadyn any jerge anda da mana borc edi berme
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            sana on kimis da bir belibav.</l>
                        <l n="12" xml:id="Sam2-018-012"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty ol kisi Joʾavɣa da jezli men
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            elcesijdim uvuclarym istine min kimis sunmaɣyjdym qolumnu uvluna ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            meleḫnin ki qulaqlarymyzca zynharlady ol meleḫ sana da osol Avišajɣa da osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            Itajɣa ajtadoɣac saqlanyz kimde tijmeske ulanɣa Avšalomɣa.</l>
                        <l n="13" xml:id="Sam2-018-013"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">או </foreign>
                            Jemese
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            qylsyjdym ʒanymda jaltajlyq da hec nerse jasyryn tivildi ol meleḫten da sen
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            turɣyjdyn jyraqtan.</l>
                        <l n="14" xml:id="Sam2-018-014"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty Joʾav tivil alaj tezermen alnynda senin da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            aldy ic cybyqlar uvucuna da qadady alarny jiregine Avšalomnun hanuz ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            bolɣanynda tiri ortasynda ol lipanyn.</l>
                        <l n="15" xml:id="Sam2-018-015"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויסובו </foreign>
                            Da qursadylar on negerler
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            eltivciler savutlaryn Joʾavnyn da vattylar osol Avšalomnu da eltirdiler
                            any.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                        <l n="16" xml:id="Sam2-018-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויתקע </foreign>
                            Da tartty Joʾav byrɣyɣa da qajtty ol ulus quvmaqtan Jisraʾel
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            artyna ki ajady Joʾav osol ol ulusnu.</l>
                        <l n="17" xml:id="Sam2-018-017"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקחו </foreign>
                            Da aldylar osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            Avšalomnu da tasladylar any ormanda ol ullu cuhurɣa da turɣuzdular anyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            istine obasyn taslarnyn ullu astry da bar Jisraʾel qactylar
                            catyrlaryna.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                        <l n="18" xml:id="Sam2-018-018"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואבשלום </foreign>
                            Da Avšalom aldy da turɣuz<addSpan spanTo="#Sam2-018-add002" />d<anchor
                                xml:id="Sam2-018-add002" type="addSpan" />u ezine tirliklerinde osol ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            macevany ki enisinde ol meleḫnin ki ajtty joḥtu mana uvul saɣyndyrmaq
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            icin atymny da atady macevaɣa aty byla ezinin da atady anar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            Jad<ref n="1" target="#Sam2-018-fn1" type="noteAnchor" /> Avšalom ol
                            uspu kingedejin.</l>
                        <l n="19" xml:id="Sam2-018-019"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואחימעץ </foreign>
                            Da Aḥimaʿac uvlu Cadoqnun
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            ajtty juvurajym endi da ḥabar berejim ol meleḫke ki tere etti H
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            any qolundan dusmanlarynyn.</l>
                        <l n="20" xml:id="Sam2-018-020"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty anar Joʾav tivil ḥabar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            kisisi sensen ol uspu kinni da ḥabar berisen ezge kinde da uspu kinde
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            ḥabar bermessen ki anyn icin ki uvlu ol meleḫnin eldi.</l>
                        <l n="21" xml:id="Sam2-018-021"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            Joʾav Kušluɣa barɣyn anlatqyn meleḫke neni ki kerdin da basurdu Kušlu Joʾavɣa
                            <milestone unit="page" n="93r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            da juvurdu.</l>
                        <l n="22" xml:id="Sam2-018-022"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויוסף </foreign>
                            Da arttyrdy daɣyn Aḥimaʿac uvlu Cadoqnun da ajtty
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            Joʾavɣa da bolsun nede juvurajym endi daɣyn mende ol Kušlu artyna da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            ajtty Joʾav nege bu juvurasen uvlum da sana bu ḥabar usamajdy.</l>
                        <l n="23" xml:id="Sam2-018-023"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויהי </foreign>
                            Da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            bolsa nede juvurmen da ajtty anar juvurɣun da juvurdu Aḥimaʿac jolu byla
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            ol majdannyn da asty ol Kušlunu.</l>
                        <l n="24" xml:id="Sam2-018-024"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ודוד </foreign>
                            Da David oltururedi ol eki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            qabaqlar arasyna da bardy ol qaravcu cardaɣyna ol qabaqnyn ol qalaɣa da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            ketirdi osol kezlerin da kerdi da muna kisi juvurady jalɣyz ezi.</l>
                        <l n="25" xml:id="Sam2-018-025"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקרא</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            Da caɣyrdy ol qaravcu da anlatty meleḫke da ajtty ol meleḫ eger jalɣyz ezidi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            ese ḥabardy avzunda anyn da bardy bara da juvuqlana.</l>
                        <l n="26" xml:id="Sam2-018-026"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וירא </foreign>
                            Da kerdi ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            qaravcu ekinci kisi juvuruvcu da caɣyrdy ol qaravcu ol qabaqcyɣa da ajtty
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            muna kisi juvurady jalɣyz ezi da ajtty ol meleḫ daɣyn buda ḥabar
                            berivcidi.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                        <l n="27" xml:id="Sam2-018-027"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty ol qaravcu keremen men osol juvurmaɣyn ol burunɣunun juvurmaɣy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            kibik Aḥimaʿacnyn uvlunun Cadoqnun da ajtty ol meleḫ jaḥsy kisidi bu da jaḥsy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            ḥabar byla keledi.</l>
                        <l n="28" xml:id="Sam2-018-028"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקרא </foreign>
                            Da caɣyrdy Aḥimaʿac da ajtty ol meleḫke bazlyqny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            da basurdu meleḫke izleri byla jerge da ajtty maḥtavludur H Tenrin senin
                            ki cyɣara
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            berdi osol ol erenlerni ki ketirdiler qol bijimde ol meleḫte.</l>
                        <l n="29" xml:id="Sam2-018-029"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            Da ajtty ol meleḫ bazlyqtymo ulanɣa Avšalomɣa da ajtty Aḥimaʿac kerdim
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            ol jyjynny ol ullu ki kleredi ijme qulu ol meleḫnin Joʾav da osol
                            qulunnu da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            bilmedim nedi.</l>
                        <l n="30" xml:id="Sam2-018-030"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty ol meleḫ qajyrylɣyn turɣun bunda da qajryldy da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            turdu.</l>
                        <l n="31" xml:id="Sam2-018-031"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והנה </foreign>
                            Da muna ol Kušlu keldi da ajtty ol Kušlu ḥabarlansyn bijim ol meleḫ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            ki tere etti seni H bigin qolundan bar ol turuvcularnyn senin
                            istine.</l>
                        <l n="32" xml:id="Sam2-018-032"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            Da ajtty ol meleḫ Kušluɣa bazlyqtymo ulanɣa Avšalomɣa da ajtty ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            Kušlu bolɣajlar ulan kibik dusmanlary bijimnin ol meleḫnin da bar kim ki
                            turdular senin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            istine jamanɣa.</l>
                        <l n="33" xml:id="Sam2-018-033"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וירגז </foreign>
                            Da acyrɣandy ol meleḫ da mindi cardaɣyna ol qabaqnyn da jylady
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            da bulaj ajtyredi jirigeninde uvlum Avšalom uvlum uvlum Avšalom kim bersijdi
                            <milestone unit="line" xml:id="Sam2018-P93r-L26" n="26"
                                next="TKow.02.003.019.xml#Sam2019-P93r-L26" />
                            elgenimni menim senin ornuna Avšalom uvlum uvlum.</l>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
